oai_dc:dc.dc:title: Large framed photograph of William Gannaway Brownlow
oai_dc:dc.dc:description: Oversized framed photograph of a young "Parson" Brownlow. Purchased at estate sale from George T. and Helen Brownlow Fritts, direct descendants. 30" x 20" Brownlow looks to be in his 30s or 40s and is seated at a desk in a chair.
